data.description: This lovely single-family residence presents a harmonious blend of modern design and thoughtful features. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, this home is designed for both family living and entertaining. Interior highlights include a an open floor plan that maximizes space and master bathroom w/ ensuite and walk-in closet. The kitchen is adorned with top-notch appliances, including a dishwasher, dryer, gas oven/range. Additional amenities feature a 2-car attached garage and a basement, ensuring that every aspect of this home has been meticulously crafted for modern living.
